{"tid":1053812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(講就兇狠 做就錄撚系列）急症科醫學院譴責醫生濫藥 醫委會：不能容忍","createTime":"2019-03-09T11:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T11:12:04.000Z","uid":167451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"deb9b11bed4fde7ce6cf48356ec0f04fee60b05d","tid":1053812,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】屯門醫院一名急症科男醫生涉嫌當值期間吸食大麻，昨日被捕，已獲准保釋，下月上旬向警方報到。消息指，這名48歲副顧問醫生的尿液樣本，被驗出懷疑大麻成份。香港急症科醫學院但譴責所有濫用藥物的醫生，在當值期間濫用藥物更加不可接受，不會評論任何正在接受警方調查的案件。<br />\n<br />\n學院指，呼籲所有醫生注意個人身心健康，若遇上精神壓力困擾，應適時尋求專業人士協助，又相信每一位在前線工作的醫生都緊守崗位，竭力維護公衆健康。<br />\n<br />\n醫委會主席劉允怡回應事件時稱，如屬實是嚴重問題，強調「不會容忍」。劉允怡又稱，相信是首次有醫生當值期間懷疑濫藥，即使警方調查後不落案起訴，醫委會收到警方證據後，亦會進行紀律聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打算拖幾多年先紀律聆訊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:-<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%80%A5%E7%97%87%E7%A7%91%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%BF%AB%E8%97%A5-%E9%86%AB%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D-081100650.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%25A7%2591%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E8%2597%25A5-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%25BF%258D-081100650.html&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ua7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=dd096833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%80%A5%E7%97%87%E7%A7%91%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%BF%AB%E8%97%A5-%E9%86%AB%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D-081100650.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c5c26c7a47bade0541ce54d9030e283ea3ba153","tid":1053812,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}